text: Olga Danilović and Marta Kostyuk were the defending champions, but both players chose not to participate. Top seeds Cori Gauff and Caty McNally won the title, defeating Hailey Baptiste and Dalayna Hewitt in an all-American final, 6–3, 6–2. == Seeds == == Draw == ===Finals=== ===Top half=== ===Bottom half=== == External links == * Main draw Girls' Doubles US Open, 2018 Girls' Doubles
